Name: [TC-1] Testing dengan lender existing [1]
Description:
1. Melakukan login dengan user existing.
    2. Cek Menu Profile Agreement -> Subscription Agreement
    3. Cek Menu Profile Agreement -> Lender - Borrower Agreement
    4. Cek Menu Profile Agreement -> Old Agreement

    *** Kodisi saat ini ***
    Menambahkan manual folder / file agreement di [bucket-renovation-test].

    *** Skenario Result ***
    1. Passed, berhasil download document agreement di url [bucket-renovation-test] 
    2. Memberikan screenshot pages dan berhasil melampirkan url [bucket-renovation-test]
    3. Memberikan lampiran database [inhouse-agreement],[funderportal] dan [profile_db]
    

    Langkah-langkah ini meliputi ...

    3. Cek Menu Profile Agreement -> Lender - Borrower Agreement
    4. Cek Menu Profile Agreement -> Old Agreement

    *** Kodisi saat ini ***
